==Dialogues==
When spoken to, the Black Guard Berserker will say one of the following:
*"Obey the law!"
*"I'm keeping an eye on you!"
*"Stay out of trouble!"
*"Out of the way, human!"
*Sometimes he will ignore the player and said player will receive the message: "The guard ignores you."

